{
  "stem": "12051.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He poked me on my shoulders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said, Gerda, I am your Papa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't recognize him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was swollen from hunger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[SIGHS] [SOBBING] And my biggest regret is, to this day, that I have hurt him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That I am his only daughter, and I didn't recognize.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I am sure that it hurt him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But maybe he forgave me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because I am alive, and he is not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] From Plaszow, we were sent--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For five minutes, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only a few minutes because Goeth was driving around in his car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, well, through the window, he was shooting everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a social club that you could stand and talk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did-- they were watching us, whatever you were doing, or whatever you talked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or-- it, it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I am terribly sorry that I did that to him, but not knowingly and, and not intentionally.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just-- that was part of the miseries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] From Plaszow, [SIGHS] we were sent to Skarzysko-Kamienna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were in a cattle train for 36 hours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't sit down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were standing one next to the other, 36 hours, without water, without facilities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whoever could, survived it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we arrived in Skarzysko.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The camp itself, the factory-- that was an ammunition factory-- was inside the woods.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We walked the whole night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When we jumped off from the train, many of us, their legs were so swollen that they twisted their ankles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to give support to those that couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we arrived the factory, oh, it was twilight and were a lot of light there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was sand in front of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
